Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:22.028 --> 00:00:23.888
What are you preparing today?
Stuffed Crab.

00:00:25.060 --> 00:00:27.214
Ingredients required to prepare Stuffed Crab :

00:00:27.877 --> 00:00:34.642
Crab, Onion, Crab Shell, Cashewnuts, Ginger-Garlic paste

00:00:35.348 --> 00:00:40.560
Garam Masala, Cumin seeds, Curry leaves, Turmeric powder

00:00:40.971 --> 00:00:44.396
Red Chilli powder, Salt, Oil.

00:00:56.514 --> 00:00:57.370
Cook the Crab legs.

00:01:56.476 --> 00:01:58.844
Once the Crab legs are cooked, seperate the meat.

00:02:13.611 --> 00:02:15.265
Heat Oil in a pan.

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:18.141
Add Cashew nuts.

00:02:21.782 --> 00:02:23.495
Add Curry leaves &amp; saute well.

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:26.962
Add Cumin seeds.

00:02:29.383 --> 00:02:31.670
Add finely chopped Onions.

00:02:36.326 --> 00:02:37.445
Add a pinch of Turmeric powder.

00:02:39.154 --> 00:02:41.665
Add Ginger-Garlic-Poppy seeds paste.

00:02:49.641 --> 00:02:51.313
Add Salt to taste.

00:02:54.694 --> 00:02:57.061
Add Red Chilli powder.

00:02:58.502 --> 00:03:00.212
Add Garam Masala.

00:03:05.381 --> 00:03:07.236
Add the cooked Crab meat.

00:03:21.543 --> 00:03:24.292
Fill this in Crab Shells.

00:03:37.347 --> 00:03:39.315
Heat water in a thick pan.

00:03:47.203 --> 00:03:50.807
Steam cook these stuffed Crab Shells.

00:04:10.192 --> 00:04:13.107
Once cooked, shift these to a serving plate.

00:04:18.278 --> 00:04:20.754
Garnish with Coriander leaves.

